cards.helptext:
These fields are used to help determine site access permissions.

If a Land Manager's account has the area filter applied, then they will have access to any sites whose County, FPAN Region, or Management Area values match up with those Management Areas added to their account. While these fields are geographical in nature, in some cases database admins will need to augment their values to handle edge cases.

If a Land Manager's account has the agency filter applied, they will have access to any site whose Management Agency matches the agency that is added to their account.
